Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.67,0:00:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起邁向自由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我們有不同的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但其實我們是一體的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.98,0:00:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希比安的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是可以把我們分開的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍色的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.99,0:00:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後是黑色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.99,0:00:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後就是被分開的兩顆心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.91,0:00:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳...妳是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.60,0:00:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和妳一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同樣被爸爸所呼喚著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.93,0:00:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.02,0:00:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.75,0:00:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳是否不喜歡女性？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打開妳的心窗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道更多妳的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\bord2\fs32\fscy81\shad2}YU-NO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,字幕檔製作：Clive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二幕 [不連續体のコンチェルト]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.97,0:01:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近有很多原居民反對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.77,0:01:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要求把劍之岬的發掘工程中止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.97,0:01:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們每天在抗議的事，你知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而這項工程的負責者就是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.68,0:01:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很明顯，她發掘到甚麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有，你居然知道...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.06,0:01:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的ID
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.99,0:01:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣我才可以知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.91,0:01:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是全靠你，拓也君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒甚麼\N實際上我沒有打算過要幫妳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:58.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，這石頭是甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.32,0:02:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這城市留下來的印証
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在劍之岬上是不可侵犯的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.45,0:02:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命之火...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳想做甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊，美月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞由美...已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳放鬆好了，我倆一起的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不以媽媽的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做回普通的女人就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.69,0:02:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求妳，美月，請住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳來這裡是做甚麼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:47.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞由美只是為了找他的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他？誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:52.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳在隱瞞甚麼？美月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花這麼多資金發掘這個山洞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對如我這種窮人來說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有錢人所想的，真是難明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們，在那裡做甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比想像中來得快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.94,0:03:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到這地步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞由美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我吧，拓也君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.37,0:03:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要那石頭做甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:03:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道妳是不會信我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞由美小姐，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓也君...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要走了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再試多一次嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是時間回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼，妳明天來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果妳希望的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等妳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:04:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約定的東西呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要心急
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先讓我沐浴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密碼我上次已經告訴過妳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個隨妳喜歡用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還未證實，這樣好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.41,0:05:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想妳知道我相信妳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次我所說的儲物櫃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會把戰利品放在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然，要等我想要的東西到手後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳真小心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是專業的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請小心保管它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特別是要注意水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯...知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼，慢慢享用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀...是了，這是我借來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是太短了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動一下就會走光的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:06:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人被人看是榮譽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡，那傢伙去了哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我應該問她的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣？全身沒力...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳是...波多乃...神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳是...誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是應該由爸爸你自己去找的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以做的就只有等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等你，爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上去準備早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上會做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就那樣失去知覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精力虛耗過度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體無法支持
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近發生了甚麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.65,0:07:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我身邊發生的到底是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概我沒有甚麼可以幫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最多只能告訴你這些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好味嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才妳所說的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡沒有任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為只有我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我媽媽死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親...雖然在我附近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他一點也記不起我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:40.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鑰匙可以的話，請放在郵箱裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等...等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個重要的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真倒霉...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:58.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成沒人可以依靠似的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.19,0:09:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,定可吸引到很多阿伯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀，是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波多乃真是穿甚麼都一樣好看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是店內最受歡迎的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳的制服是境町學院的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在在那裡就讀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島津這個人妳知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是理事長的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.75,0:09:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這樣，難怪這麼富有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波多乃，妳有客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳打算就這樣子去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然，我會穿裙子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這個，是運動褲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.77,0:10:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣才能讓人客開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊，原來這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進去了一直沒出過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能這裡就是她的...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.80,0:10:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼波多乃會...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.84,0:10:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波多乃神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個有很多謠傳的女孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們先去吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳知道妳自己在做甚麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了生活，這是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停止啊，總之先把衣服穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要我的就只有那裡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:10:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.92,0:11:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是唯一接觸這世界的媒介
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世界是甚麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了你，我失去了客人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為補償，請你抱我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來不是那指環
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這世界的神秘力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只有這等程度嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真令人失望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,澪，是澪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.89,0:11:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到神奈也擁有這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳怎麼怪怪的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳真是澪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說甚麼？我一直是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它給我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能給妳，這等於我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.83,0:12:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住...住手啊，澪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要阻我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是...究竟發生甚麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓也這白癡...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下亞由美一個人，自己去哪裡玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞由美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直很緊張亞由美的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這時候就連人影也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞由美小姐，我...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了甚麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然應該叫豐富君送我一程
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那...那是甚麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.24,0:12:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦，我好像聽到甚麼似的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:03.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時空轉移...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有鑰匙也可以...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請離開這裡，有馬先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她現在並不是普通的她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下，究竟發生甚麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧？爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.71,0:13:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是妳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為在短時間內
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.11,0:13:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現了多次的時空轉移
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以因子出現了不安定，爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，爸爸是在叫我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸就是爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該差不多習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體覺得怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繪里子老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到妳的內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來沒甚麼大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:13:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波多乃和澪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道，不要問我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我走了，我正在散步途中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是在家裡做家課的時候了\N少年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間的...不，自修的學習
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明聽到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝醉酒找男人真是差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且妳已經這把年紀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了，妳的內褲，姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳好像一個人很寂寞，沒有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對妳研究的東西很有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.98,0:14:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳肯把ID告訴我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:15:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在車裡面也是不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們究竟在做甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來阿姨級也不是沒看頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不只是成熟的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.51,0:15:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寡婦，寡婦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭，有點臭臭的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我們玩過後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳馬上就可以忘記死去的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們這麼做，究竟為了有甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是為了錢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們對這方面很在行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我能停止她們之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.70,0:15:44.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳還是告訴我妳的ID比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，我是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，妳們...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:16:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我究竟做錯了甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，沒用的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.59,0:16:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美月小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:12.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候你應該去陪亞由美的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是你又要去陪你的大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了甚麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得好點了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:30.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝你，豐富君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請喝，這樣可以讓精神放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼找到我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.76,0:16:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很清楚妳的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去換衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豐...豐富君...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道原來妳穿得這麼可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很想看妳穿了這個後的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.81,0:17:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣可以讓我感覺到妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.72,0:17:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，在這種時候...真卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.80,0:17:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人對女人所做的都是卑鄙的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要...住手...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不開心的事，快點忘記比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚的事也...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死去的丈夫的事也...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.74,0:17:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不...不行啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，把腿張開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳不照我的話去做嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:17:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就對了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我來幫妳忘記不開心的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豐富...君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了，我...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓也...君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不遲不早的救了妳？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.81,0:18:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種人妳也可以相信嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.81,0:19:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞由美小姐妳被騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被騙其實也是一種幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.84,0:19:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那種獨立的女人，我不夠堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是，為甚麼不找我？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.25,0:19:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是你的媽媽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.77,0:19:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和情人不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身為一個女人\N有些事是不能跟你說的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣...我...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了嗎？小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞由美已經不需要你幫助了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎？亞由美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是已經...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.39,0:19:49.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是，不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓也君的幫助，已經不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.60,0:19:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以被迷惑的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.72,0:19:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波多乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:20:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人正在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在很遠的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在等爸爸的拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，沒有人在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.71,0:20:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我抱住時那種陶醉，你也看到吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞由美的事，你就忘記了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.32,0:20:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以忘記的，爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘記了就永遠見不了面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那個人也...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽也...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有YUNO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,YUNO？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.61,0:20:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點把那石頭交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.76,0:20:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,澪，已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又消失又出現的，你也很忙呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的澪小姐\N並不是你所認識的澪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我應該怎樣做？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.59,0:20:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼會變成這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒有必要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在沒有鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如再失去那石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.80,0:21:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經不可以再進行時空轉移
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都會回復正常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.41,0:21:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不會有人受苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.53,0:21:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳不這樣認為嗎？神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，波多乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.46,0:21:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道有一個方法可以救澪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.80,0:21:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在就幫妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.80,0:21:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,澪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有馬...君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.80,0:22:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.25,0:22:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳究竟是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.80,0:22:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有馬先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.97,0:22:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著的...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.27,0:22:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著的拜託了，爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.80,0:22:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波多乃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.50,0:22:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波多乃，振作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.40,0:22:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有了那石頭的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子已經...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.00,0:22:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有馬先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.78,0:22:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.60,0:22:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.20,0:22:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.70,0:22:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我第一次害怕死亡
